[ctns_make id='gen_abs_opposite_of']

  [ctns_front style='']
Opposite of $$x$$
  [/ctns_front]  

  [ctns_back style='font-size:140%;']
$$-x$$<br/><br/>$$x+(\red{-x})=0$$
  [/ctns_back]  

  [ctns_frontspeak]
Opposite of x
  [/ctns_frontspeak]  

  [ctns_backspeak]
The opposite of x is negative x so that the sum of x plus its opposite equals zero.
  [/ctns_backspeak]  

[/ctns_make]
